https://spring.io/blog/2019/10/15/simple-event-driven-microservices-with-spring-cloud-stream

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Switch between Brokers
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Create 1 CloudStream Application and bind Kafka or Rabbit with a maven
property

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spring Cloud Function Support
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Defined Supplier bean is automatically called every second and written
to the "output" MessageChannel

